{"tid":744064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡斯拿斯怒斥球證：法國「罰球+12碼」不存在！","createTime":"2018-07-15T17:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T17:44:47.000Z","uid":186431,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b95adebee2c5787103955da2e21d2dd9485a1c1c","tid":744064,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"世界盃決賽，法國對克羅地亞的比賽一波三折。法國隊先是憑藉克羅地亞的一個烏龍球獲得領先，但克羅地亞很快扳平比數，而比賽接近半場休息時，克羅地亞又送出了一個12碼。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　比賽第38分鐘，基沙文右側開出角球，馬杜迪前門柱爭頂，球蹭比列錫偏出近門柱，法國隊員抗議比列錫手球，慢鏡顯示球碰了比列錫左手，阿根廷球證皮塔納求助於VAR，親自到場邊觀看重播後補吹12碼。　　<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　前西班牙國門卡斯拿斯對球證皮塔納的判罰表示了不滿：「又一次錯誤！比列錫無法去掉手臂。馬杜迪想要頭槌，結果判斷失誤，未能頭槌。比列錫碰到了皮球，對我來說，這不是12碼。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　卡斯拿斯還對視頻球證系統的運用表示了不滿：「老實說，我不能很好地理解視頻球證系統的使用。球證判罰了一次對基沙文的不存在的犯規，法國隊憑藉此次行動取得入球。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20180716/9031926/?cf=fb_hk_soccer&amp;u=peter&amp;st=JdnEyh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsoccer.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2F1%2F20180716%2F9031926%2F%3Fcf%3Dfb_hk_soccer%26u%3Dpeter%26st%3DJdnEyh&d=Ykw%2FkmxHp4xjGoUCFxxyAjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=097242ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://soccer.sina.com.hk/news/1/20180716/9031926/?cf=fb_hk_soccer&amp;u=peter&amp;st=JdnEyh</a>"},{"pid":"cadb58cc96530b3ee7f982d90ec1b0e9b517fe49","tid":744064,"uid":47268,"like":16,"dislike":42,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩<br />\n過氣龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52720a781cce5aa938b64f9a1a6d2746f2cc9fd","tid":744064,"uid":3194,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"cadb58cc96530b3ee7f982d90ec1b0e9b517fe49","tid":744064,"uid":47268,"like":16,"dislike":42,"score":-26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩<br />\n過氣龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm